      • toUserString

        public String toUserString()
        Returns a string representation of the object, that can be displayed to the user. It is formated as:
        • "fullyQualifiedMethod(fileName:lineNumber)"
          if fileName != 0 and lineNumber >= 0

        • "fullyQualifiedMethod(Unknown Source)"
          if fileName == 0 or lineNumber < 0
        See Also:
        Object.toString()
